  <div class="teaser-date">05/13/25</div>
  <h4 class="teaser-headline">
      <a href="/article/lhc-near-miss-collisions-turn-lead-into-gold?language_content_entity=und" rel="bookmark"><span>LHC near-miss collisions turn lead into gold</span>
</a>
  </h4> 
  <p>In a recent study, ALICE scientists measured the way that lead ions colliding in the LHC sometimes transform into gold and other new nuclei.&nbsp;</p>

</article>
</div>

    </div>
  
          </div>
</div>

  </div>

  </div>
</div>
</section>


